title: Free Agent RBs, latest Antonio Brown drama with Sean Wagner (Football 2/20)
description:
Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including Antonio Brown's meeting with the Steelers and possible landing spot for Colin Kaepernick as well as taking a look at the free agent NFL running backs.
